---
title: Grilled Chorizo Kibbeh-Inspired Bowl with Chopped Salad and Bulgur Pilaf
description: Inspired by the classic mezze meatball-like dish of spiced meat mixed with bulgur, without all the fiddly assembly! Flavourful Turkish Spice blend and red onion add savoury flavours to chorizo.
